responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D8D48FCB461F7E80A7055DA7E87DBC14", "Come and dance five sisters of Sephillion. Dance the dance and wish for me. Helea my dearest, what wonders do you wish to see? I dream of glint heavy and free. A personal hoard piled high and only for me.")
